description:
&lt;p&gt;Enabling, Caring, Team working, fast moving, sometimes challenging, always inclusive, if this sounds appealing to you then we may have the opportunity that you have been waiting for at Sidmouth Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To work in a ward environment specialising in rehabilitation of the elderly. Would you like to be more involved in an &quot;Enabling Ethos&quot; with a great multi-disciplinary team, and superb community connections? Then we may have the position for you. Working together to provide the right environment to support people using a strength based approach to regain as much independence as possible, with a primary aim on returning to their own home, or original place of residence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therapy team, community volunteers, and medical team, as well as our social care colleagues and families and carers all working alongside each other to promote a culture of enablement, putting the person at the centre. Utilising goal setting that are relevant to the person, and will support them to return home or place of choice. The pace is fast, and an element of creativity, and a want to make a difference, to support people back to their home is vital. Your nursing skills will work to compliment the therapy and social skills, ensuring that the people we care for, are helped to optimise their health and well being.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For informal conversation or visit please contact Toni Sutherland, Clinical Nurse Manager Sidmouth CH on 07970180101&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our vision is to provide safe, high quality seamless services delivered with courtesy and respect. To achieve our vision we expect all our staff to uphold our Trust values. Our Trust values are: &lt;br /&gt; Honesty, Openness &amp; Integrity&lt;br /&gt; Fairness&lt;br /&gt; Inclusion &amp; Collaboration&lt;br /&gt; Respect &amp; Dignity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;***Preference will be given to staff with ‘Priority’ and &#39;At Risk&#39; status including NHS At Risk staff throughout Devon.***&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DUE TO THE ANTICIPATED HIGH NUMBER OF APPLICATIONS FOR THIS POST WE RESERVE THE RIGHT TO CLOSE THE VACANCY BEFORE THE CLOSING DATE.&lt;/p&gt;
